### Register a new customer user
POST https://localhost:7154/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@example.com",
  "username": "customer1",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": 0
}

###

### Register a new admin user
POST https://localhost:7154/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "username": "admin1",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": 1
}

###

### Login as customer
POST https://localhost:7154/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "customer1",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login as admin
POST https://localhost:7154/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin1",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Get user profile (requires authentication)
GET https://localhost:7154/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Check token status (requires authentication)
GET https://localhost:7154/api/auth/token-status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Access protected data (requires authentication - any role)
GET https://localhost:7154/api/protected/data
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Access admin-only data (requires Admin role)
GET https://localhost:7154/api/protected/admin
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Access customer-only data (requires Customer role)
GET https://localhost:7154/api/protected/customer
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CUSTOMER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Logout (invalidate token) - requires authentication
POST https://localhost:7154/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Try to access protected data after logout (should fail with 401)
GET https://localhost:7154/api/protected/data
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Try to access admin data with customer token (should fail with 403)
GET https://localhost:7154/api/protected/admin
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_CUSTOMER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Try to access customer data with admin token (should fail with 403)
GET https://localhost:7154/api/protected/customer
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ADMIN_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get weather forecast (original endpoint, no auth required)
GET https://localhost:7154/WeatherForecast

